Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.51,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When the Cherry Blossoms Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What beautiful weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pink cherry blossoms,\Na blue sky, and white clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing like eating rice balls\Nunder cherry blossom trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, give me one more rice ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Which kind do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:02:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, fish flakes, and a chicken nugget, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The petals have mostly fallen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I think I like it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't so crowded,\Nso you can view them in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Rei has arrived in Yamagata yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe. I bet this is the best time\Nto see them over there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Human Shogi is so artistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}They wear armor and kimonos\Nand hold it in a big park, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I bet it looks beautiful\Nunder cherry blossom trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Cherry blossoms in full bloom,\Nthe beautiful blue sky, green mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Lucky him. It sounds so romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like I said. I'm a rain-bringer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cut out for outdoor festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I'm already feeling shameful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:03:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because I had straight losses at the Lion King\NTournament and couldn't bring the match here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Chairman...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine! Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just go and let everyone cheer you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean that kind of cheering up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This lonely melody echoing through\Nan empty train station!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why this tune?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bad omen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}From the City of Shogi, Tendou,\NLet's Get a Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What could I say to apologize?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all so kind that I know\Nthey would never blame me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that makes it more painful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would rather...\NI would rather have them berate me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You rain-bringer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do about this rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This weather is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You rain-bringer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That being said, I'm being berated\Nfive seconds after getting here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, hand out towels to the Pawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, have a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shimada 8th-Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shiono Club
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new recipe from the Shiono Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,French whale rice cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious. This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, this is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I was gonna make a bundle\Nselling the new product.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:55.29,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stab\NStab
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:55.29,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grumble\NGrumble
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- But with this rain, it's a wash-out!\N- I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Kiddo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That suits you. It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were born to wear that, Kiddo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It suits him so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's like the daimyou, Shingen himself!\NLike a full-sized Boys' Festival doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've touched this old man's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So where's your opponent, Yokomizo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And he's like, um... Kobayakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takakage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hideaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's with that obscure lineup?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:46.38,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,42nd Tendou Cherry Blossom Festival\NHuman Shogi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}42nd Tendou Cherry Blossom Festival\NHuman Shogi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now, Yokomizo 7th-Dan\Nhas the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7-f-Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.62,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White\NHarunobu Nikaidou\N5th-Dan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.62,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black\NOkuyasu Yokomizo\N7th-Dan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Nikaidou 5th-Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3-d-Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6-f-Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8-d-Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6-h-Rook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.23,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40 Minutes Later
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, next, 6-g-Silver...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot that a Lance moved up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In Human Shogi, there's a rule,\Nor goal rather, to move all of the pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a different type of fight,\Nso it's easy to miss something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then the same, Bishop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, 3-e-Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Slice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! A move that takes advantage\Nof his opponent's error!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the 42nd Human Shogi game,\Nthe winner after 96 moves
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is Nikaidou 5th-Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.\NI'm extremely delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Harunobu, that was marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good game, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take a breather, Kobayakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying it on purpose, Mr. Hanaoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Next up is the 100 Move event.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman, Nikaidou,\NOkuyasu and I are participating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman, you're in the program,\Nso you can't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, I...\NMy stomach is kind of hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you from the hallway excitedly\Ntalking about having Yonezawa beef tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All of the participants are looking forward\Nto beating you, Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I learned my lesson last year.\NThese people are unusually good players.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the old folks who are in\Nthe club you formed, Shimada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even the old lady over there\Nwould open with a Castle like it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That just isn't normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't finish the game in two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Yonezawa beef will get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it, too. Mr. Tsujii was complaining\Nabout doing it last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said he got whipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsujii, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In his greeting at the opening ceremony,\Nhe pulled a fast one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, people of Yamagata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love me Tendour...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am Takeshi Tsujii.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think the locals would be\Nthat put off by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he said that.\NThere was never any question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Mr. Tsujii is on stage,\Nhe's going to say a pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}42nd 100 Move Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's time.\NPlayers, thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the ever-popular 100 Moves event.\NAnd here are our professional shogi players.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, everybody! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Harunobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shiono Club
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okuyasu, get in front of the Shiono Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. These people have come\Nto beat you, Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, how about if I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shiono Club
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, grandmas and grandpas.\NI'm not going to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have it any other way!\NYou're gonna miss dinner tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to eat dinner, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I came all the way back home,\Nso let's all eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. That makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of Shimada 8th-Dan's\Nhometown, Kiriyama 5th-Dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh... Have I met him somewhere before?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Izumida with the Yamagata Journal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He did an article on Mr. Shimada.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:11:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Um, I really get the feeling that everyone\Nhere is a strong supporter of Mr. Shimada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada 8th-Dan's real hometown\Nis more in the back regions of Yamagata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As the population declines,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,seniors living by themselves get isolated in\Ntheir homes in the winter because of the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was troubled by that,\Nso he created the Shiono Shogi Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shiono Club
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twice a week, a bus goes around to all\Nthe seniors' houses to pick them up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and they play shogi\Non kotatsus at the community center.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,While some play shogi, others cook\Nnon-perishable food for the group in large pots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And when it's time to go home, they take with\Nthem the daily necessities or ingredients
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they'd asked for as a group,\Nas he arranged to buy it for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada 8th-Dan is trying to arrange for\Nthe elderly people to not feel isolated anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:12:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada 8th-Dan also made\Nthe arrangements to sell
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the non-perishable food and sweets\Nthe Shiono Club makes to the train stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most wonderful of all is how these activities\Nhave made the old folks so spry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, sorry. I didn't mean to bend your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all! I'm glad you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Shimada has been depressed lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He wonders how he can apologize to everyone\Nregarding the Lion King Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, seeing him smile like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it makes me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been covering him all this time for the\Nnewspaper, so I've become totally enamored.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I totally understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Mr. Izumida said that and smiled,\Nhe seemed delighted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That kind of made me happy too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt connected to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that feeling somehow filled me with joy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here's bakke miso, rice balls, snow greens\Npickled in salt, and whale rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And here are some frozen dried persimmons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are giving me so much again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're never gonna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're never gonna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No need to rush, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been rushing so much that I lost my head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How many times do I go back\Nto where I started?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was so lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:14:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even from here on out,\Nthat feeling won't go away, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Shimada! The train's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Hurry up, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}From the City of Shogi, Tendou,\NLet's Get a Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll start over again this year\Nand work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's gonna be scary,\Nbut you should pass through.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should pass through.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.99,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When the Cherry Blossoms Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:37.00,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Small Murmur
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mikazuki Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem troubled, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about your next new creation, Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm trying to think of something\Nthat'd be good for the summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not getting any inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:15:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Baked Crescents are great\Nand have become the shop's signature sweet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but if possible,\NI'd like one more new showpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then the name and form should be easy\Nfor people to remember, and don't get tired of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But will also keep for a few days\Nso it'd be good as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So something baked?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Long-lasting is important too, but if it's baked,\Nit'll overlap with the Baked Crescents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we can go with something that's fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like the strawberry daifuku, which doesn't\Nhave a long shelf life, but is popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strawberry daifuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised the first time,\Nbut it turned out well and caught on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So something like the\Nstrawberry daifuku with an unexpected filling
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and if we can get a new flavor, that'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay Hina, for example,\Nwhat filling would make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, let's see... Like apples...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and whipped cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whipped cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:15:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Whipped cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I think putting whipped cream in Japanese-style\Nsweets would kill the merit of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just think that could be heresy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But bean paste and whipped cream\Nare delicious together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, like cream mitsumame\Nor cream red bean soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, cream mitsumame is good\Nwith whipped cream on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cream mitsumame, huh?\NIt really is tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help dropping in\Nat Flower Garden or Mitsuhashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But sweets shops are traps, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sweets Mitsuhashi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should we get a sweet treat\Nbefore going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to splurge once in a while, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the mitsumame is only 350 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Glitter\NGlitter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd want to put sweet beans on top, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Huff\NHuff
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that would be anmitsu for 430 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's okay.\NFor the two of us, it'd be 860 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Dazzle\NDazzle
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But wait! In that case, for another 100 yen,\Nwe can have it with cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:17:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Huff\NHuff
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! Cream would be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if we're going that far, another 50 yen\Nwould get us whipped cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Dazzle\NDazzle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! If we're putting whipped cream on top,\NI'd want apricots, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll have bananas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ta-daaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Packed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}In the end,\NAll the toppings
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.20,DefaultLow,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Total: 1,610 Yen
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sweets Mitsuhashi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this always happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We spent 1,610 yen on just a snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stuffed. I'm gonna get fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm always stingy to a fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With 1,610 yen, we could've bought\N2.3 kg of chicken at 68 yen per 100 grams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With 2.3 kg, we could've fed\Nthe family for five days!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sale
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sweets shop traps are scary!\NYour mind goes blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you get fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is our punishment\Nfor going without Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now we've got to be even more frugal\Nthis month. I regret what we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't get depressed over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:18:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was that something recent? I thought you were\Ngoing to help me come up with a new idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Momo!\NHow about you, Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What filling would you like in a rice cake?\NWhat do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gum?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a genius here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- G-Grandpa! Get a grip!\N- Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, calm down.\NCalm down and we can think it through again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Shh, shh, okay, okay.\N- Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A tasty filling for a daifuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}First, red bean paste, of course.\NAnd sweet green paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Walnuts, matcha, apples, strawberries...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chestnuts, sweet potatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salted caramel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And whipped cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go too far from the Japanese confections!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I went along with what you're saying,\Nthis would turn into a cake shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you kids actually hate Japanese sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! I really like it! I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't narrow it down!\NThere are too many choices!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet green paste, matcha cream,\Nstrawberry cream, chestnut...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Woman want this and that, and are so greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't pick one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So many different flavors...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a daruma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sangatsu-chou Puffy-Puffy Daruma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The rice cakes are filled\Nwith different flavors of bean jam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and when put together, look like snowmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Good Fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Puffy" can also mean "good fortune,"\Nand I used it twice to double the good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two flavors of bean jam\Nin a set and they're cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet green paste and whipped cream\Nor sweet red bean paste and sweet potato...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can make variations\Nby changing just the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice to change the flavors\Nwith the seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like limited time flavors...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chestnut paste in the fall,\Nstrawberry cream in the spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll tell Sada\Nand the others about it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta be positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, look.\NI thought up of a sweet, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chomp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's eating me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mom came up with the Baked Crescents, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm the one who worked hard to make the\Nprototype, the mold, and the finishing touches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the one who thought up the cute shape\Nand name was your mom, Mikako.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:21:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mikako loved cooking, loved Japanese sweets,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and would learn by watching others, then make\Ndifferent "prototype" sweets on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I hope this Puffy-Puffy Daruma makes\Neveryone happy, just like the Baked Crescents.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I can't wait for everyone to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing for us yet-meow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come over for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Yes. I'd love to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, Rei. Long time no see.\NHow have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Was the Human Shogi fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yes. It was raining, but still fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, what's all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mentor shared it with me.\NFrom his hometown in Yamagata.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said he couldn't eat all of it,\Nso offered me some.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, come in, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.18,0:22:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That day, Kiriyama brought over\Nall kinds of goodies from Yamagata.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sis was thrilled the side dishes\Ncrossed the bridge and made it over to us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We also enjoyed the Puffy-Puffy Daruma\NI came up with for dessert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And this is still a secret, but if I can, I'd like\Nto make Japanese sweets for a living{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday run the shop with Grandpa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:22:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hinata.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Small Murmur
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:36.18,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 22
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.47,0:24:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just pursuing the truth!\NDon't falter, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.18,0:24:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is shogi that minor?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.39,0:24:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There are limits\Nin making snap decisions, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.48,0:24:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I'm gathering natto.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.44,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can we eat together?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.90,0:24:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I was definitely a guy\Nwho can bring out the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.28,0:24:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For next year's Human Shogi,\NI've decided that it's going to be sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.70,0:24:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode\Nof "March Comes in Like a Lion"!
